data.description: Beautiful fenced home in the historic Old Seminole Heights area in the heart of Tampa! Spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with detached 2 car garage accessed through the side gate. This home has numerous updates including brand NEW IMPACT DOUBLE PANE HURRICANE WINDOWS 2022, AC 2021, ELECTRIC updates and CIRCUIT BREAKER BOX 2022, NEW SEWER LINES (all new), Roof 2014. Split Bedroom Floor Plan, updated kitchen with custom Wood Cabinets, Granite Counter Tops and Stainless-Steel Appliances 2021 and updated Bathrooms. Spacious fenced backyard with plenty of room for entertaining and to park an RV, boat or your favorite toys. Large Carport and driveway in front of the home for additional parking. Desirable location with easy access to the Hillsborough River and the beautiful Lowry Park, the Lowry Park Zoo and a newly built Public Boat Ramp. Just minutes away from all the new restaurants and breweries in Seminole Heights, Ybor City, downtown Tampa. I-275 and I-4. No HOA, no CDDs. This home is the perfect retirement home, vacation or rental. VISIT OUR 3-D TOUR.
